==English==
===Etymology===
From the Old English ''[[cote]]'', the feminine form of ''[[cot]]'' "small house."

===Pronunciation===
*{{SAMPA|/"kot/}}
*{{IPA|/'kot/}}

===Noun===
'''cote'''
# A small [[structure]] built to contain [[domesticated]] [[animal]]s such as [[sheep]], [[pig]]s or [[pigeon]]s.

